Brix/Octociz looked around for what he could do, and than saw it.

"Kepp doing that, but be careful. What I'm about to do might do the 
trick.:

Brix/Octociz turned on his jets and started going up. Up and up, 
until finaly he had cleared the trees into the blue. He estimated 
where the three bots were, and drew his rocket launchers.

"I'm sure you've killed millions of bots. This is for all of them."


He went headfirst back into the forest. He was right about where the 
bots were. He started firing his rocket launchers towards them at 
point blank range.

"DIE SCUM!!!"

A slight anger began to take over Brix's body......
